TWEEPOLL

This repository contains all the necessary pieces of codes to our project.
Please see the report for more information.

Here is a description of each file:
- Tweepoll - Final Report: Report that describes in detail our project
- training_data: data capture (from twitter) for the training set
- sample_data: data capture for the sample set. This set is used to make the actual poll.
- queries: mongodb queries to perform the bag of words (including the cleaning process)
- dataset_building: Construction of the training dataset from the mongodb bag of words
- dataset_building_sample: Construction of the sample dataset from the mongodb bag of words
- classifier: Comparison of different classifiers on the dataset
- prediction: Final prediction on the sample
- stop_words: The chosen list of stop_words for this project
